    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Financial Support: As per SWC contract.\r\n\t\r\n\t\tTechnical Support: As per need\r\n\t\r\n\t\tTraining: \r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\tTraining for the Team of Educators and Social Workers\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\tThe team of educators and social workers of VOC is highly motivated and all possess a great sensitivity to the problems of these children. Follow-ups and training sessions have allowed to evaluate their performance level, as well as to develop their capabilities and desire to progress.\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t \r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\tStreet children project\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\tSeveral training sessions will be conducted either by external organizations or by EED. It aims at strengthening the capacity of VOC's educators, social workers and managers. The trainings topics could cover child development, child sexual abuse, language development, computer and language skills, etc.\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\tPrevention project\r\n\t\tThe FDP approach has been successfully implemented in countries such as Cambodia and Philippines, but is quite new to Nepal. This new approach is being introduced by VOC, and hence, the staff from VOC will need to be trained on this new methodology.\r\n\r\n\r\n\t \r\n\r\n\t\r\n\t\tFollowup, Supervision and Monitoring: As per the provision in the agreement."
      },
      "ne": null
    },
